com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.session
Class SessionManagerPropertiesImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.session.SessionManagerPropertiesImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SessionManagerProperties, SessionPoolProperties, SessionProperties
public class SessionManagerPropertiesImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements SessionManagerProperties, SessionPoolProperties, SessionProperties

A SessionManager is configured based on a SessionManagerProperties instance. This class loads properties from a properties file and presents a guaranteed minimum set of properties to be available to the SessionManager and its SessionPool.
